Package: humanleague
Type: Package
Title: humanleague: a synthetic population generator
Description: Generates integer synthetic populations given integer marginal data, in up to 12 dimensions, using quasirandom without-replacement sampling. Also provides a quasirandom sequence generator and a function to convert discrete marginal probabilities into integer frequencies.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrew Smith
Maintainer: Andrew Smith <a.p.smith@leeds.ac.uk>
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
